{
  "id": "greeting-valentine",
  "name": "情人节贺卡",
  "category": "greeting",
  "description": "一张浪漫的情人节贺卡，带有飘动的心形和玫瑰装饰",
  "trigger": {
    "type": "date",
    "conditions": [
      {
        "type": "date_match",
        "value": "02-14",
        "description": "情人节当天触发"
      },
      {
        "type": "relationship",
        "operator": ">=",
        "value": 80,
        "description": "好感度达到80以上时可能触发"
      }
    ]
  },
  "variables": {
    "recipient": {
      "type": "string",
      "description": "收卡人名称"
    },
    "sender": {
      "type": "string",
      "description": "送卡人名称"
    },
    "content": {
      "type": "text",
      "maxLength": 400,
      "description": "情人节祝福内容"
    }
  },
  "promptTemplate": "请生成一段情人节祝福语。\n\n背景信息：\n- 送卡人：{{sender}}\n- 收卡人：{{recipient}}\n- 关系：{{relationship}}\n- 相识时间：{{meetingTime}}\n\n要求：\n1. 内容浪漫深情，表达爱意\n2. 语气要符合送卡人的性格特点\n3. 可以提及两人之间的甜蜜回忆\n4. 字数控制在100-200字之间\n5. 要有浪漫氛围感\n\n请直接输出祝福内容，不要有其他说明。",
  "style": {
    "theme": "romantic",
    "colors": ["#ff6b6b", "#ff9a9e", "#fecfef"],
    "mood": "浪漫甜蜜"
  },
  "rarity": "seasonal",
  "collectible": true
}